com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast

Class TLIf

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast.TLElement
      • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast.TLCondStmt
        • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast.TLIf

  • public class TLIf
extends TLCondStmt
    TLElement that represents a If conditional statement. It's a TLCondStmt characterized by:
    • a TLExpression representing a condition
    • a list of elseif blocks as a list of TLIf
    • a block as a list of TLElement
    • an else block as a list of TLElement
    • a flag to keep track if it's an else if statement
    • a flag to keep track if it's written using the ternary operator
